IFPREVERB CLIMB 0
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR SKILL5 > 4
    GMMSG The thief made it in by climbing the wall to the second floor.
    ECHO PLAYER You look up and down the wall for hand and foot holds.
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT 
    ECHO PLAYER You think you find the perfect path to take.
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER You begin your climb to the window, you reach up for the last hand hold and......
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT 
    ECHO PLAYER you make it! You slowly crawl through the window to the inside.
    MOVE 437
  ELSE
    GMMSG The thief tried to climb the wall without the proper skill.
    ECHO PLAYER You look up and down the wall for hand and foot holds.
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER You think you find the perfect path to take.
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER You begin your climb to the window, you reach up for the next hand hold....
    PLREVENT 2
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO PLAYER but you lack the proper training, you foot slips and fall to the ground.
    DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 15 Ouch that hurt!
    POSITION LAY
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The window is to high on the wall.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB SMELL -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You cant seem to place the smell but it is getting stronger as you move on.
ENDIF
